The paper proposes a novel algorithm for multi-label learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The algorithm involves gradient descent and transfer learning techniques, which are commonly used in subfields such as deep learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
